Package camzup.kotlin

Class KtMat3

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Mat3
camzup.kotlin.KtMat3
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<KtVec3>
public class KtMat3
extends Mat3
implements java.lang.Iterable<KtVec3>
Provides Kotlin operator overloading support for three dimensional matrices.
